Hello,

I hope you are doing well.

I was applying for GSoC 2026 under the EROFS organization and had prepared
my proposal for the project *=E2=80=9CAdvanced Fuzzing and Image Injection
Framework for EROFS.=E2=80=9D* Unfortunately, due to a last-minute submissi=
on
issue, I missed the official deadline by a very small margin (around one
minute).

I completely understand the importance of deadlines, but I wanted to
sincerely request if my proposal could still be considered. I have invested
significant effort into understanding the project, designing a detailed
solution, and preparing a structured plan.

I have attached my full proposal for your review. I would truly appreciate
any consideration or feedback you could provide.

Regardless of the outcome, I am very interested in contributing to EROFS
and would be happy to stay involved with the project.

Thank you for your time and understanding.

Best regards,
Daksh Garg

